00:31:16,940 --> 00:31:19,870
doesn't even have
the courage to face difficulties.

564
00:31:20,370 --> 00:31:21,200
Ms. An.

565
00:31:21,460 --> 00:31:22,180
Keep it up.

566
00:31:23,810 --> 00:31:24,770
You too.

567
00:31:25,200 --> 00:31:27,370
You look gentle,

568
00:31:27,760 --> 00:31:29,490
but you're very strong inside.

569
00:31:30,080 --> 00:31:33,190
Watching you go from housekeeping
to the front desk step by step,

570
00:31:33,190 --> 00:31:35,870
and maybe even higher
and further in the future,

571
00:31:36,770 --> 00:31:38,790
I feel greatly encouraged.

572
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:44,960
[Jiang Zhichun]

573
00:31:43,480 --> 00:31:44,680
Are you free tonight?

574
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:45,890
Let's meet up.

575
00:31:46,260 --> 00:31:47,560
I need to talk to you.

576
00:31:50,370 --> 00:31:52,430
The news lately has been terrifying.

577
00:31:52,950 --> 00:31:54,610
It puts everyone in a bad mood.

578
00:31:55,130 --> 00:31:56,650
Someone died here.

579
00:31:57,040 --> 00:31:59,120
[Are you free tonight? Let's meet up.
I need to talk to you]

580
00:31:57,120 --> 00:31:58,920
This used to be a popular photo spot.

581
00:31:58,920 --> 00:31:59,720
Now look at it.

582
00:31:59,740 --> 00:32:01,000
No one dares to go.

583
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:02,200
What's wrong?

584
00:32:04,680 --> 00:32:06,430
There is a top-rated scenic spot

585
00:32:06,430 --> 00:32:08,690
with a glass walkway tens of meters long.

586
00:32:08,850 --> 00:32:10,200
[Glass Walkway Failure
Causes a Tourist to Fall Down Mountain]

587
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:10,680
It allegedly malfunctioned,

588
00:32:10,220 --> 00:32:11,360
[Famed Foliage
and Snow Destination in Crisis]

589
00:32:10,700 --> 00:32:12,530
causing a tourist to fall off the cliff.

590
00:32:11,390 --> 00:32:12,240
[Recently at the famous
top-rated scenic spot,]

591
00:32:12,260 --> 00:32:13,370
[a heartbreaking accident occurred]

592
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:15,240
This place used to be super crowded.

593
00:32:15,350 --> 00:32:16,310
People enjoyed the snow in winter,

594
00:32:16,310 --> 00:32:17,710
and the leaves in autumn.

595
00:32:17,850 --> 00:32:18,440
Right.

596
00:32:18,750 --> 00:32:20,750
Dianjiangchun promoted this place before.

597
00:32:20,750 --> 00:32:22,950
Maybe she's the one who made it popular.

598
00:32:23,680 --> 00:32:24,240
Really?

599
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:25,270
Look.

600
00:32:25,270 --> 00:32:28,600
Why is everyone mentioning
Dianjiangchun in the comments?

601
00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:32,580
The scenic spot had an accident.

602
00:32:32,580 --> 00:32:33,860
Why are they scolding the blogger?

603
00:32:32,890 --> 00:32:33,430
[Comments]

604
00:32:33,450 --> 00:32:34,540
[Dianjiangchun, don't you
have any responsibility?]

605
00:32:34,560 --> 00:32:35,300
[Doesn't your conscience bother you?]

606
00:32:37,070 --> 00:32:38,100
[Unknown Caller]

607
00:32:42,800 --> 00:32:43,880
Some netizens are going too far.

608
00:32:43,880 --> 00:32:44,400
Hello.

609
00:32:44,610 --> 00:32:46,560
Mr. Ji, could you please come over?

610
00:32:47,430 --> 00:32:48,150
What is it?

611
00:32:48,740 --> 00:32:50,540
Zhichun is being cyberbullied.

612
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:51,960
The board is going to abandon her.

613
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:53,270
None of us can reach her right now.

614
00:32:53,270 --> 00:32:55,330
I had no choice but to ask you for help.

615
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:57,360
Okay, don't worry.

616
00:32:57,380 --> 00:32:58,510
I'll be right there.

617
00:33:00,950 --> 00:33:03,690
[Jiang Zhichun]

618
00:33:05,640 --> 00:33:07,000
I'm heading out for a bit.

619
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:08,600
Call me if you need anything.

620
00:33:37,710 --> 00:33:38,510
Zhichun.

621
00:33:42,670 --> 00:33:44,110
I was wondering before,

622
00:33:46,090 --> 00:33:47,570
if I disappeared,

623
00:33:50,050 --> 00:33:53,010
would you be the first one to look for me?

624
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:56,430
It seems I was right.

625
00:33:57,320 --> 00:33:58,760
On my way here,

626
00:33:59,180 --> 00:34:00,980
I learned about the whole thing.

627
00:34:01,600 --> 00:34:03,150
Can you come down first?

628
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:08,170
Look,

629
00:34:08,190 --> 00:34:11,239
[Resolution on the Change
of a Partner of Qiguang Media Co., Ltd.]

630
00:34:09,330 --> 00:34:11,320
I can't even rely on a promise

631
00:34:12,219 --> 00:34:14,150
that's written in black and white.

632
00:34:24,600 --> 00:34:25,989
How ironic.

633
00:34:26,409 --> 00:34:28,739
I've been an influencer for so many years,

634
00:34:28,770 --> 00:34:30,699
and this is the first time I realize

635
00:34:31,500 --> 00:34:33,500
the weight of the word "influence".

636
00:34:33,639 --> 00:34:34,969
The Jiang Zhichun I know

637
00:34:36,210 --> 00:34:37,650
would never give up so easily.

638
00:34:37,650 --> 00:34:39,070
You've made it this far.

639
00:34:39,340 --> 00:34:41,600
Are you really afraid of cyberbullying?

640
00:34:41,820 --> 00:34:43,679
I'm not afraid of cyberbullying.

641
00:34:44,719 --> 00:34:45,870
But some people are.

642
00:34:47,650 --> 00:34:48,730
Can you imagine?

643
00:34:49,850 --> 00:34:52,030
The partners you spend every day with,

644
00:34:52,030 --> 00:34:53,489
once they are on the board,

645
00:34:54,290 --> 00:34:55,429
drop their smiles

646
00:34:56,670 --> 00:34:59,000
and try to strip you
of your partner title.

647
00:35:00,550 --> 00:35:03,180
I founded this company myself.

648
00:35:03,470 --> 00:35:05,250
Why should I be pushed out?

649
00:35:05,410 --> 00:35:06,860
Why should I be the sacrifice?

650
00:35:06,860 --> 00:35:08,130
Exactly, why?

651
00:35:08,750 --> 00:35:10,830
Giving up on yourself here

652
00:35:10,910 --> 00:35:12,690
doesn't hurt them at all.

653
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:15,580
You, Jiang Zhichun, are so competitive.

654
00:35:15,630 --> 00:35:18,190
In the past, you were always
the one who did the leaving.

655
00:35:18,190 --> 00:35:20,630
Are you willing to become a discard now?

656
00:35:23,290 --> 00:35:24,290
Don't worry.

657
00:35:26,440 --> 00:35:27,540
Jiang Zhichun

658
00:35:28,970 --> 00:35:31,500
won't easily become
someone else's discard.

659
00:35:54,150 --> 00:35:54,960
Ji Feng.

660
00:35:56,690 --> 00:35:57,650
I'm sorry.

661
00:35:58,320 --> 00:36:01,580
I've thought about it
countless times recently.

662
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:06,320
If only I weren't so selfish.

663
00:36:09,650 --> 00:36:12,210
If only I could turn back time.

664
00:36:21,600 --> 00:36:25,790
[Director Tang]

665
00:36:23,030 --> 00:36:24,000
Director Tang.

666
00:36:24,190 --> 00:36:25,340
How does the internal transfer process

667
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:27,540
work between departments at our hotel?

668
00:36:34,850 --> 00:36:39,810
[Director Tang]

669
00:36:35,380 --> 00:36:37,430
Ms. Xu, do you want to transfer?

670
00:36:37,630 --> 00:36:39,000
If you want to transfer
from your position,

671
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:40,400
it requires
the general manager's approval.

672
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:41,190
Oh my god.

673
00:36:41,360 --> 00:36:42,320
Mr. Ji and Dianjiangchun

674
00:36:42,320 --> 00:36:43,920
are not really together, are they?

675
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:45,280
Of course they are.

676
00:36:45,510 --> 00:36:48,970
They have been going in and out
of the same apartment together.

677
00:36:54,140 --> 00:36:55,890
[Dianjiangchun]

678
00:36:58,920 --> 00:36:59,400
[Following the sudden accident caused
by the glass walkway malfunction,]

679
00:36:59,420 --> 00:36:59,850
[the issue gained traction online,
and influencer]

680
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:00,190
[Dianjiangchun
was thrust into the spotlight.]

681
00:37:00,220 --> 00:37:01,460
[As the public awaited her response
to questions about the promotion,]

682
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:02,950
[a set of photos quickly
spread online, showing]

683
00:37:02,970 --> 00:37:04,450
[Dianjiangchun and Ji Feng entering
and leaving a luxury apartment together.]

684
00:37:04,470 --> 00:37:05,070
[Netizens questioned whether,
during the promotion, Dianjiangchun]

685
00:37:05,100 --> 00:37:05,780
[had thoroughly assessed
the safety of the site's facilities,]

686
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:06,600
[and whether her promotional content
may have misled consumers.]

687
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:38,080
I...

688
00:37:41,770 --> 00:37:42,750
Listen to me.

689
00:37:44,090 --> 00:37:45,980
I made things clear to her today.

690
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:47,320
Between the two of us...

691
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:47,920
Then why were you

692
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:48,880
photographed going in

693
00:37:48,880 --> 00:37:50,440
and out of her apartment?

694
00:37:50,510 --> 00:37:52,150
Is this what you mean
by making things clear?

695
00:37:52,150 --> 00:37:54,080
I was afraid you'd misunderstand.

696
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:55,840
It was an emergency today.

697
00:37:56,120 --> 00:37:58,030
Her assistant called me to help.

698
00:37:58,130 --> 00:38:00,480
I didn't expect it
to blow up like this online.

699
00:38:00,480 --> 00:38:04,070
-Trust me, between us...
-This isn't the first time this has happened.

700
00:38:04,070 --> 00:38:05,630
If drawing a clear line with your ex

701
00:38:05,630 --> 00:38:07,230
is this hard for you,

702
00:38:07,230 --> 00:38:08,800
maybe you should ask yourself

703
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:10,800
whether you still have feelings for her.

704
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:12,130
It's not what you think.

705
00:38:12,510 --> 00:38:13,480
Listen to my explanation.

706
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:15,150
Enough, you don't need to say anything.

707
00:38:15,150 --> 00:38:17,350
Actually, there's nothing to explain.

708
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,920
We are both adults.

709
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:20,860
You are single, and I am divorced.

710
00:38:22,880 --> 00:38:25,340
If this is the kind
of relationship you want,

711
00:38:26,400 --> 00:38:28,000
you can just tell me clearly.

712
00:38:30,070 --> 00:38:30,670
By the way,

713
00:38:31,230 --> 00:38:32,280
I will probably submit an application

714
00:38:32,280 --> 00:38:34,630
for a cross-department transfer soon.

715
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:37,080
Mr. Ji, you will need to approve it then.

716
00:38:49,150 --> 00:38:50,480
What is wrong with me?

717
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:53,440
Why did I say those things to him?

718
00:38:54,590 --> 00:38:57,090
I don't want to see myself
lose control like this.

719
00:38:57,090 --> 00:38:58,840
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

720
00:38:58,440 --> 00:38:59,670
Maybe this is the reason why I'm afraid

721
00:38:59,670 --> 00:39:01,710
to fall in love with someone again.

722
00:39:00,600 --> 00:39:02,240
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

723
00:39:03,250 --> 00:39:05,710
Mr. Ji, were you acquainted
with Ms. Jiang before?

724
00:39:04,460 --> 00:39:06,240
♪ People in the city ♪

725
00:39:05,710 --> 00:39:06,920
We...

726
00:39:07,190 --> 00:39:10,130
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

727
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:09,780
Were college classmates.

728
00:39:10,030 --> 00:39:12,070
[Set aside longing for the past;
kindle a new fire and savor fresh tea]

729
00:39:12,060 --> 00:39:13,870
♪ The palms of time ♪

730
00:39:12,090 --> 00:39:13,100
[Enjoy poetry and wine
in the prime of life]

731
00:39:15,790 --> 00:39:18,830
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

732
00:39:18,420 --> 00:39:20,490
Are the two of you dating?

733
00:39:19,520 --> 00:39:22,050
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

734
00:39:20,880 --> 00:39:22,000
We...

735
00:39:22,410 --> 00:39:23,410
Used to be in love.

736
00:39:23,460 --> 00:39:25,630
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

737
00:39:23,590 --> 00:39:24,510
What about me?

738
00:39:25,150 --> 00:39:26,240
Can't I ask you out?

739
00:39:27,220 --> 00:39:30,270
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

740
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:29,550
Their creamy pasta

741
00:39:29,570 --> 00:39:30,850
is still your weakness, huh?

742
00:39:30,750 --> 00:39:33,780
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

743
00:39:31,990 --> 00:39:32,630
[Netizens questioned whether,
during the promotion, Dianjiangchun]

744
00:39:32,650 --> 00:39:33,470
[had thoroughly assessed
the safety of the site's facilities,]

745
00:39:33,490 --> 00:39:34,520
[and whether her promotional content
may have misled consumers.]

746
00:39:34,370 --> 00:39:37,490
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

747
00:39:38,230 --> 00:39:40,850
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

748
00:39:42,270 --> 00:39:45,460
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

749
00:39:45,340 --> 00:39:46,550
Don't you know?

750
00:39:46,130 --> 00:39:49,580
♪ The forgotten past ♪

751
00:39:48,930 --> 00:39:50,240
Because I like you.

752
00:39:50,490 --> 00:39:52,760
♪ Walking through this world ♪

753
00:39:54,410 --> 00:39:58,430
♪ Leaving no regrets behind ♪

754
00:39:59,070 --> 00:40:00,600
[Tan Jizhou]

755
00:40:01,490 --> 00:40:02,320
Hello.

756
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:05,250
Miyu, can we talk?

757
00:40:18,350 --> 00:40:19,140
Mr. Tan.

758
00:40:19,630 --> 00:40:21,030
Last time you asked me out,

759
00:40:21,030 --> 00:40:22,230
I couldn't make it.

760
00:40:22,360 --> 00:40:23,110
I'm sorry.

761
00:40:24,600 --> 00:40:27,000
Actually, I should be
the one to apologize.

762
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:28,890
In Hong Kong,

763
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:31,400
I was too abrupt. I'm sorry.

764
00:40:32,640 --> 00:40:35,430
I drank too much that day too.

765
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:39,280
Actually, I thought about it
for a long time after I went back.

766
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:41,010
I got ahead of myself last time.

767
00:40:42,190 --> 00:40:44,480
Relationships should develop naturally.

768
00:40:44,480 --> 00:40:45,810
We should take our time.

769
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:49,840
So, Miyu,

770
00:40:51,190 --> 00:40:51,840
may I...

771
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:54,440
May I pursue you?

772
00:41:09,150 --> 00:41:10,760
I've actually imagined many times

773
00:41:10,760 --> 00:41:12,630
what it would be like if we were together.

774
00:41:12,630 --> 00:41:14,920
I could talk about art with you,

775
00:41:15,280 --> 00:41:17,360
take you to exhibitions
all over the world,

776
00:41:17,360 --> 00:41:19,220
and give you everything you want.

777
00:41:19,590 --> 00:41:20,510
All you need to do is stay

778
00:41:20,510 --> 00:41:21,630
by my side.

779
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:23,880
So Miyu,

780
00:41:24,930 --> 00:41:26,130
can you give me a chance?
